findings.title: Missing Emergency Handling
findings.description: In WusdAlpacaStrategy contract, there is no function to execute emergencyWithdraw() of Alpaca FairLaunch contract, causing $USDT to be stuck when an emergency case occurs.

findings.title: Redundant Calling of onlyOwner Modifier
findings.description: Removing `onlyOwner` modifier from functions to adhere to coding standards.
